reviews.text: One of my favorite places for tasty Chinese food. It was so tasty. The service here is better than most. Prices were reasonable. I see why this place has a lot of great reviews.

Good for delivery Chinese food. Their sesame sauce is super good. Love the hot and sour soup. Is it the best I ever had no. Is it good for quick lunch or your craving Chinese and want it delivered yes. It does take time for delivery.

Well where to start,  we ordered a Coke and a Dr. Pepper.  We got 2 glasses of ice and two cans of soda. Wow! The food is edible however I have certainly had much better but I have also had worse. Would I recommend this restaurant or will I be returning? NO!
Great place for tasty Chinese food. Got there near five, it wasn't very busy. Next time I'll be back with my relatives. Prices are fair.
Clean place, good Chinese (I recommend the steamed pork dumplings), and decent service. Mostly a take out place, but comfortable enough if you want to eat in.
